{
  "stem": "7458.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And from being a very bad student in the Hebrew school, I became an excellent student in the Russian school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I learned Russian very quickly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I had excellent marks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And as a reward, I was elected to be the president of a pioneer group.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Now the-- in the Soviet system, young children were pioneers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They wore red scarves and a pin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "From pioneer, when you went into high school, you joined the Komsomol.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And from the Komsomol, if you were a good, obedient member, eventually you joined the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So I was a pioneer, and president of the pioneer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I loved it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And again, life was wonderful for me as a child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My father was not deported.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We were allowed to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We were allowed to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] benefit from some of the technological improvements that the Russians had brought.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And all in all, it was not bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish institutions were affected, most of them, actually, for the better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did not do away with the Yiddish library.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They discouraged religion against all people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Religion was the opium of the people, according to communist doctrine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it wasn't a strict enforcement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews were still able to pray, still have-- had their institutions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were still able to celebrate the holidays of Passover and all the others.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at the same time, we were given a chance to join some aspects of Soviet society.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it-- it wasn't terribly oppressive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only for those who were very rich or those who had committed crimes, they were strict.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But other than that, it was not bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] nobody really knew what the pact between Stalin and Hitler was, or what it meant.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
